<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>3</hymn_number>
<title>zǒu xiàng guāng míng 迦南3</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men cóng hēi àn zǒu xiàng guāng míng, cóng sǐ wáng zǒu xiàng yǒng shēng
 wǒ men hái yǒu shén me yuán yóu zài zhè lǐ chí chí bù xíng.
 shēn biān jì yǒu zhè xǔ duō de jiàn zhèng jiù dāng bèi qǐ shí jià yǔ zhǔ tóng xíng
 zài wǒ men miàn qián yǒu shén dài lǐng, qǐng nǐ bù yào kǒng jù zhàn jīng.</lyrics>
</song>